reviewText: Great deal. If you like goofy comedies, snag this bundle!

The 5-star rating is for getting what I expected. I had seen all of these movies on cable before and knew they were not what critics would praise. I specifically bought this boxed set for "Grandma's Boy", the movie that demonstrates how low older former stars, in this case Shirley Jones, will stoop just to make a living.
What can I say? The movies are great. The delivery was fast.
Fun to watch and not as outlandish as other B movies
Grest laughs watching these old movies!!
